Package: SpaCCI
Type: Package
Title: Spatially Aware Cell-Cell Interaction Analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-08-29
Author: Li-Ting Ku
Maintainer: Li-Ting Ku <lku@mdanderson.org>
Description: SpaCCI provides tools for analyzing spatial cell-cell interactions based on ligand-receptor pairs. The package includes functions for local, regional, and global analysis of cell-cell communication using spatial transcriptomics data. It integrates with the CellChat, CellPhoneDB, Cellinker, ICELLNET, and ConnectomeDB database for identifying possible ligand-receptor pairs, visualizes interactions through heat map, chord diagrams, and includes methods for inferring interactions on different spatial scales.
